window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Friends in despair, a goddess in distress, and a mountain of problems to resolve.</b></p> <p>Damien isn't one to shy away from combat or protecting those he holds dear, and for a long time now, he hopes to find some peace and quiet. Outside forces threaten to rip his happy ending away, becoming both a bane, and a focus of his wrath.</p> <p><b>Join Damien on the series conclusion.</b></p>"; 
